[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 141     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m         J --> K[Lambda: Solution Parser]
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 142     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m         K --> L[DynamoDB: Proposed Schedule]
