[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      409[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             ASSIGN block to best_service
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      410[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             NOTIFY scheduling team via SNS: "Block released to {best_service}"
[0m[49m[39m  396, 411[0m:[39m[49m 
